pullRequest.title: delete timeseries when path is not found
pullRequest.bodyText:
Problem >>> If the DeleteTimeseriesPlan is routed globally and the metadata is removed, and the other node needs to retrieve the full paths, then the metadata is nowhere to be found.
Solution >>> In this implementation, the full paths will be retrieved before plan routing.
